520
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:33,230
Excuse me!

521
00:27:56,460 --> 00:27:57,930
Oh, I am sorry.

522
00:27:59,770 --> 00:28:01,230
Good you came. 
What's with you?

523
00:28:01,230 --> 00:28:03,070
How come you are here?

524
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:07,110
Don't tell me... you're this family's lost son?

525
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:08,210
Who are you?

526
00:28:08,210 --> 00:28:09,310
You know me?

527
00:28:09,310 --> 00:28:10,780
What?

528
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:13,710
Hongberg... Isn't it you?

529
00:28:13,710 --> 00:28:14,810
Am I not right?

530
00:28:14,810 --> 00:28:15,920
No.

531
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:17,380
Seeing you say no, I know it's you!

532
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:20,320
What's this? You are going to act dumb?

533
00:28:20,320 --> 00:28:22,890
Why were you throwing so much stuff
onto the door like that?

534
00:28:22,890 --> 00:28:23,990
Some toilet paper...

535
00:28:23,990 --> 00:28:25,440
Toilet paper?

536
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:28,030
