I too wanted to try it once.

539
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,370
Wait a moment.

540
00:28:35,370 --> 00:28:37,060
You sonofa...

541
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:48,580
What are you doing?

542
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:53,720
Some toilet paper... She said there's no
toilet paper in the washroom.

543
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:55,190
I will give it to her.

544
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:58,860
Yes.

545
00:28:58,860 --> 00:29:01,060
I'm sorry.

546
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:04,730
Hey, can't you get it fast--

547
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:06,570
I'm sorry.

548
00:29:06,570 --> 00:29:07,670
I'm throwing this.

549
00:29:07,670 --> 00:29:09,870
Thank you.

550
00:29:10,970 --> 00:29:12,440
Embarrassing.

551
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:16,110
Really, the lost son in their house
is our next-door youngster?

552
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:18,680
I told you it's true!
I was also flat-out shocked.

553
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:20,510
How is this possible?

554
00:29:20,510 --> 00:29:21,980
What to do about this now?

555
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:23,820
What do you mean what to do?

556
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:25,650
Hello.

557
00:29:25,650 --> 00:29:27,120
I saw you going into this place.

558
00:29:27,490 --> 00:29:28,590
Ajumma, have you been doing well?

559
00:29:28,590 --> 00:29:31,890
Yeah... But how did this happen to you?

560
00:29:31,890 --> 00:29:33,360
Are you really a son in this family?

561
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:34,830
No, I'm not.

562
00:29:34,830 --> 00:29:37,030
How? I hear you are.

563
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:38,860
What a world!

564
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:44,370
Somehow, right from start, I was totally
getting the feeling that you were
totally of a dignified pedigree.

565
00:29:44,370 --> 00:29:46,570
At first you reported me as a
murder suspect, you know.

566
00:29:46,570 --> 00:29:48,770
It was this girl who reported you!

567
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:50,980
What is with this girl?

568
00:29:50,980 --> 00:29:54,650
I can care less if you're the son here or not. 
Can't you call saying you're leaving, you bastard?

569
00:29:54,650 --> 00:29:55,750
Why now, about that...

570
00:29:55,750 --> 00:30:00,150
Without toilet paper, I wasn't thinking earlier,
so I forgot to kick your ass there.
But I just remembered.

571
00:30:00,150 --> 00:30:01,250
Step out with me.

572
00:30:01,250 --> 00:30:03,820
You damn well tell me clearly
what crap you've been up to.

573
00:30:03,820 --> 00:30:06,390
Only you should hear that?
I want to hear too.

574
00:30:07,130 --> 00:30:10,430
So I was with the people at
the private detective center.

575
00:30:10,430 --> 00:30:14,100
You didn't even have time for a call?
Terrible fellow.

576
00:30:14,470 --> 00:30:16,300
My mobile phone had to be changed.

577
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:18,870
I was all confused.

578
00:30:18,870 --> 00:30:21,070
At first I thought I'd call to tell you everything.

579
00:30:21,070 --> 00:30:22,910
All just talk, right?

580
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:24,740
Put in your number.

581
00:30:24,740 --> 00:30:25,850
Like it's dark right below a lamp,

582
00:30:25,850 --> 00:30:29,520
I was dumbstruck, and didn't even know
your phone number!

583
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:36,490
- Here.
- Name too!

584
00:30:36,490 --> 00:30:39,060
I was dumbstruck that I really
didn't know your name either.

585
00:30:39,060 --> 00:30:40,530
What is your name?

586
00:30:40,530 --> 00:30:43,100
Hong.

587
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:44,560
Ber-geu.

588
00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:46,400
Hongber... 
Damn you, seriously!

589
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:47,870
I'm asking what your real name is?

590
00:30:47,870 --> 00:30:49,340
Hong Bo Gu.

591
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:51,900
Hong means jewel. Bo means see.
Gu is 9. So it means "see 9 jewels".

592
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:55,570
You're lucky that I hate just 
beating people up too fast!

593
00:30:56,310 --> 00:30:57,780
Forget it. Fine.

594
00:30:57,780 --> 00:31:00,350
If you are a son of that family,
you'll get a new name.

595
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:02,550
But, do you know that it's our CEO's family?

596
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:04,750
I knew just before coming.

597
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,590
Anyway, congratulations.

598
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:08,050
You're fortunate.

599
00:31:08,050 --> 00:31:10,990
Being a son in such a rich family
simply does not fit you though.

600
00:31:10,990 --> 00:31:12,460
I won't be.

601
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:13,930
- Won't be what?
- The son.

602
00:31:13,930 --> 00:31:14,660
Why?

603
00:31:14,660 --> 00:31:15,760
Again that "Not not" disease?

604
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:17,960
No.

605
00:31:19,430 --> 00:31:22,000
But I wouldn't be.

606
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:24,940
Really.

607
00:31:30,080 --> 00:31:33,750
Oh... The Near-U software you installed here
can be deleted, I think.

608
00:31:33,750 --> 00:31:38,520
The registered users are only you and me.
We have no further use for it, right?

609
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:39,250
Just leave it there.

610
00:31:39,250 --> 00:31:42,560
